{
  "stem": "1062.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember what he told me to this day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, of course, this was in Buna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And of course, the boy was hungry, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was-- you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I, by the way, looked up and I reported this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then I found out the whole story about this boy, it's story by itself, what happened to this boy and how he came Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's a story by itself, but I'm just telling you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Even though I didn't speak the language, certain things I remember, because it was said to me and I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so it was, I don't know, maybe 10, 12 days later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The train stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there were already people, skeletons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Some of them were dressed in the striped uniforms, and some of them had just plain civilian uniforms.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were already from Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were working around the camp there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they took us off the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when we came off the train, we-- one had to support other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were like-- nobody could walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You know, we had like, to support each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "With the hand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We were supporting, limping along.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they took us into the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "By the camp, there is a building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they gave me a new number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "This number was no good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My number was like, 125,000-something, and I have the number downstairs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And they told us to go down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We're going to go for a shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Now, I heard stories in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I was sure this is it, because-- and we had to walk even down to the steps, and that made it even more eerie.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There were pipes alongside there, the staircase.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we were going down and then stairs up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we went into a-- to a-- to a big room, big room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "There were shower heads in the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we're staying there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I recited Ashrei, my prayer and I knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Lo and behold, water is coming out, warm water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I open my mouth and I drank, you know, because you couldn't drink that water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was all so contaminated or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we got a shower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And after we got a shower, they took-- they were outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "They brought a big tub.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "In the tub, there was kerosene.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "One guy got a hold of the head, other guy by your feet, and they dipped you into the kerosene for disinfecting, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And I was put into a camp, into the camp, into Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "See, Buchenwald had two-- it was one big camp, but there was one camp where there was Russian prisoners of war, Norwegian.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "You know, Buchenwald was a very-- it wasn't Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "When I was there, most of the people were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "But behind the big camp, there was a little camp where the hospital was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "It was called the kleine lager or the totenlager, the small camp or the death camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "In there, where most of the Jews were kept.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "So they didn't put me in the-- in the death lager, in the death camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "I was in the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And they put me to work in Buchenwald in the quarry, which is called a Steinbruch, the Steinbruch.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "The Steinbruch was a penal for people-- it was like a penal, penal colony.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Very few people survived the Steinbruch, because what happened over there, they-- they took a big rock and they put it on you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And you had to carry it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And when you weren't up, so somebody, an SS man, would push you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And then the rock would roll down and you [INAUDIBLE] fall down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "The other guy would-- But when I was there, I met-- there was a guy who was a German civilian there who worked there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And he left me a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And I worked in the Steinbruch not much, maybe about three, four days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And from there I was taken to work on the highway near Weimar, on the main Autobahn by Weimar, passing through Weimar.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And when we went out, we went out at night, in the dark, because those days, I want you to know, this was already February, 1945, nothing in Germany moved during the day, the trains, the cars, even a horse.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Because the planes, the American planes, the British planes, were always overhead and they would shoot up anything, everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was working on the-- on the-- on the-- on the-- on the Autobahn, but I was already finished.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I couldn't walk any-- I mean, I had trouble walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was just a skeleton, nothing, nothing left.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
